          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Low-Energy Gamma Radiation from the Bombardment of",
                "Carbon by Protons"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "AUTHOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "H.H.Woodbury",
                "A.V.Tollestrup",
                "R.B.Day"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "REFERENCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "code": "J,PR,93,1311,1954",
                "code_unit": [
                  {
                    "unit": "J,PR,93,1311,1954",
                    "doi": "10.1103/PhysRev.93.1311",
                    "field": {
                      "reference_type": "J",
                      "reference": {
                        "code": "PR",
                        "number": null,
                        "volume": "93",
                        "part": null,
                        "issue": null,
                        "page": "1311"
                      },
                      "date": 1954
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "unit_combination": "(%)"
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "#doi:10.1103/PhysRev.93.1311"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "REL-REF": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "code": "I",
                "subentry_number": "C1647001",
                "author": "H.H.Woodbury+",
                "reference": {
                  "code": "J,PR,92,1199,1953",
                  "field": {
                    "reference_type": "J",
                    "reference": {
                      "code": "PR",
                      "number": null,
                      "volume": "92",
                      "part": null,
                      "issue": null,
                      "page": "1199"
                    },
                    "date": 1953
                  }
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The",
                "counter and associated electronic equipment."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INSTITUTE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "1USACAL"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "VDG"
                ],
                "institute": "1USACAL"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " California Institute of Technology 3-MeV",
                "electrostatic accelerator."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Two types of targets were used. One was prepared by",
                "holding cleaned tantalum over a smoky benzene flame;",
                "the second was prepared by cracking methane",
                " (natural gas) on a hot strip of tantalum for the",
                "preparation of C13 targets. The target thickness was",
                "found by measuring the width of the 1.76-MeV",
                "resonance in C13(p,gamma)N13. This resonance is",
                "strong enough to be easily observable in normal",
                "carbon, and since it has a width of only 2 keV, while",
                "the targets were 20 to 100 keV thick, the observed",
                "resonance width was equal to the target thickness.",
                "Knowing the target thickness in keV, one could then",
                "calculate the number of carbon atoms per square",
                "centimeter by dividing by the stopping cross section",
                "of carbon at the average proton bombarding energy",
                "used in determining the target thickness."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The scintillation spectrometer consisted of",
                "an Nal(T1) crystal 1.5, inches long and 1.5, inches",
                "in diameter mounted on a 5819 photomultiplier."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "PHWT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Since the background radiation from the",
                "electrostatic accelerator and from other reactions in",
                "the target was generally very much more intense than",
                "the gamma ray of interest here, it was necessary to",
                "identify the latter by means of its characteristic",
                "photopeak produced in the NaI(Tl) scintillation",
                "counter. Therefore, the measurements required a",
                "pulse-height spectrum to be obtained at each",
                "bombarding energy."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "To obtain the true yields it was also necessary to",
                "make a correction for absorption of the gamma rays in",
                "the target chamber. This was only 2 to 4 percent for",
                "the measurements at 90 degree, but amounted to",
                "approximately 20 percent at O degree."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "HISTORY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "date": 20200422,
                "history": "C"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " BP"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ENDBIB": {
